  ul
    li Coloured (primary)
    li Black
    li White
    li Clear
  p Buttons 
    strong must 
    | use a modifier class to select a button type. The coloured buttons are to take on the product's 
    a.underlined(href='/') colour
    | .

  .card
    .block-bot-md
      button.btn-coloured Coloured Button
      button.btn-black Black Button
      button.btn-white White Button
      .bg-dk-grey.block-xs.inline-block
        button.btn-clear.tight Clear Button
    .block-bot-md
      button.btn-coloured.btn-disabled(disabled) Disabled Button
    .block-bot-md
